      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll try to find some saline drops tomorrow. but like, what if i just do a little bit of hydrogen peroxide instead? i heard that works really well for cleaning out stuff. would that be okay to do tonight to see if it helps faster? i'm just kinda worried it's stuck in there bad.",
